* Your name is the splinter inside me *

89
00:10:49,930 --> 00:10:54,820
* While I wait *

90
00:10:57,920 --> 00:11:02,410
* And I remember the sound *

91
00:11:03,300 --> 00:11:07,190
* Of your November downtown *

92
