* And I don't have to stay this way *

96
00:11:29,400 --> 00:11:32,520
* If only I would wait *

97
00:11:33,840 --> 00:11:38,700
* The walk has all been cleared by now *

98
00:11:38,700 --> 00:11:45,080
* Your voice is all I hear somehow *

99
